The following is a list of features and associated scopes of work that must be addressed for project completion.

1) python script must be incorporated into and called by a web framework (most likely Flask)
2) create user input form that sends data to python script
3) generate emails confirming upcoming flightlog entries upon completion of above form
4) generate emails one hour prior to logged flight times
5) the script utilizes the email address yourflightweather@gmail.com and must allow python to login to email account
   without exposing password or requiring manual entry.
